    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/23036232/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/23036232/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">leibe</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-11-24"
      class="main-meta">2009-11-24 13:38:01</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2787624_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  杜庆春  黑色是单调的，也是丰富的。一块乌黑的色块是死一般的，但是如果是黑夜呢？如果这黑夜是浮出在城市的上空，涌塞住都市的街巷，有摇曳灯光和霓虹，有红唇和枪花四射，有一截可以逃亡的楼梯，有一处可以守望的窗口呢？那黑夜就是丰富的。夜晚比夜色更多，夜城比夜色更野...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">14有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
